1. Molim te, budi *oprezan* prilikom prelaska ulice. (Please be *careful* when crossing the street.)
2. Mi smo uvijek *oprezni* prilikom odabira poslovnih partnera. (We are always *cautious* when choosing business partners.)
3. Deca bi trebalo da budu *oprezna* kada se igraju sa oštrim predmetima. (Children should be *cautious* when playing with sharp objects.)
4. Ona je bila *oprezna* u svakoj fazi pregovora. (She was *careful* at every stage of the negotiations.)
5. *Oprezno* priđite ovoj krivini, jer je jako strma. (*Carefully* approach this curve, as it is very steep.)
6. *Opreznim* pokretom izvadite komad stakla iz gume. (Remove the piece of glass from the tire with a *cautious* movement.)
7. Dok vozite, morate biti *oprezni* zbog velikog broja rupa na putu. (While driving, you must be *careful* due to the large number of potholes on the road.)
8. Potrebno je biti *oprezan* prilikom izbora hrane za bebu. (It is necessary to be *cautious* when choosing food for the baby.)
9. Uvijek budite *oprezni* kada se penjete na planinu. (Always be *careful* when climbing a mountain.)
10. *Opreznošću* smo izbjegli veliku katastrofu. (We avoided a major disaster with *caution*.)